{"tid":1419041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 各層面心理準備及方向建議","createTime":"2019-08-05T23:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T00:11:51.000Z","uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ed7f49ac2be870362eed60a441b44c4ce9dc8e21","tid":1419041,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:14:17.000Z","msg":"真理越辯越明，用腦諗野，做正確既事<br />\n再多三毛五毛都係過眼雲煙<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">個人層面</span></ins></span><br />\n全民自肅，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>抑制消費</strong></span><br />\n保持抗爭心態，五大訴求同警暴問題堅持到底<br />\n除左搭車食飯，避免非必要既開支同消遣<br />\n配合中美貿易戰全球經濟下行風險<br />\n以外憂內患，為政府制定相關對策時<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>擴大缺口</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">社交平台層面</span></ins></span><br />\n繼續揭發同追究黑警問題<br />\n疑似內地執法人員等等<br />\n唔好俾<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">每日記者會</span></strong>蒙混而過<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非層面</span></ins></span><br />\n喺市區和平集會已經名存實亡<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">機場</span></strong>絕對係重要目標<br />\n由初試罷工已足見影響力<br />\n贖罪券停一停諗一諗<br />\n送到真正對象手上係少之又少<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行動派層面</span></ins></span><br />\n繼續針對目標，透過零星衝突進行快閃行動<br />\n封路封隧、圍警署等行動繼續發揮功效<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點到即止</span></strong>，同時避免完全癱瘓<br />\n保持不受傷不被捕為至高原則<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目標為本</span></strong>，掟核彈都不割<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n相關主題<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">今日三罷 無疑係失敗</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417352/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417352/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a854e15535f9b88f6a0a7fb4499e208cc5247a5b","tid":1419041,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:27:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>連儂資訊牆繼續做</ins></span></span><br />\n用標題「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>記者會不會告訴你的事</strong></span>」<br />\n係對抗每日記者會既其中一個重要渠道"},{"pid":"fc97f62021c919862ea6f2ea18e33c9921243ae2","tid":1419041,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:34:10.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"f96fea0e242f7762ea9a6a1cb63edd75a2a27304","tid":1419041,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:49:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd014512c35380e685587411152328c14352e1d6","tid":1419041,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:57:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5957d7c20a6687f24a36183e2c7bff279ef95a9f","tid":1419041,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:11:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}